snippet: Marian Gaborik’s goal at 3 minutes 29 seconds of overtime gave the Rangers a 3-2 victory, their eighth in nine games, against the the Panthers.
abstract: NHL Roundup; New York Rangers defeat Florida Panthers, 3-2, in overtime; other NHL results noted.
lead_paragraph: Marian Gaborik’s goal at 3 minutes 29 seconds of overtime gave the Rangers a 3-2 victory, their eighth in nine games, against the the Panthers.
